sentences.en: A proprietary ATC and APC circuit insure the stability output power.
sentences.cn: 输出功率的稳定性由独特设计的ATC和APC电路得到保证.

sentences.en: At the moment the technology tends to be proprietary and application - specific.
sentences.cn: 目前生物识别技术大多被专利保护,而且一种产品只有一种用途.

sentences.en: Different proprietary organic - solvent preservatives often contain the same toxicants.
sentences.cn: 不同专利的有机溶剂防腐剂往往含有相同的毒性剂.

sentences.en: Directors weren't allowed any proprietary airs about the product they made.
sentences.cn: 主管们不允许对他们生产的产品以所有者自居。

sentences.en: Doses presented in terms of the proprietary product are more meaningful to the grower.
sentences.cn: 用专利品来表示使用剂量对栽培者来说最有意义.

sentences.en: During the early years of FOIA, however , companies submitting proprietary information often felt unprotected.
sentences.cn: 在《信息自由法》的早期阶段,提供专有信息的公司常常感到得不到保护.

sentences.en: For grease marks try a proprietary dry cleaner.
sentences.cn: 若要去除油污,可以试试一种专利干洗剂.

sentences.en: He has no proprietary interest in the farm (= he does not own any part of it ) .
sentences.cn: 他对这座农场没有所有权。

sentences.en: Interferometer: Optic compensation RockSolidTM, proprietary vibration interferometer , permanently aligned.
sentences.cn: 干涉仪: 专利产品,光学补偿,永远准直, 抗振动.

sentences.en: Most state legislation is neither proprietary nor discriminatory, and thus falls into the third class.
sentences.cn: 大多数州立法既非专有性的,也不是歧视性的, 所以应归为第三类.

sentences.en: Proprietary manufacturing technology, production and operation of facilities - small, large - scale production.
sentences.cn: 拥有生产专有技术, 非生产经营性设施少, 生产规模大.

sentences.en: Retail chemicals, antibiotics, proprietary Chinese medicine, Chinese medicine Yinpian.
sentences.cn: 零售化学制剂 、 抗生素 、 中成药 、 中药饮片.

sentences.en: The company has a proprietary right to the property.
sentences.cn: 公司拥有这笔财产的所有权。

sentences.en: The conversion process is a proprietary algorithmic successive - approximation technique.
sentences.cn: 转换过程采用一种专有的逐次逼近算法技术.

sentences.en: They have proprietary rights to the data.
sentences.cn: 他们拥有那些数据资料的所有权。

sentences.en: Unfortunately, the announcement also makes it clear that the datasets are proprietary.
sentences.cn: 不幸的是, 公告还明确指出,数据集是专有的.

sentences.en: We had to take action to protect the proprietary technology.
sentences.cn: 我们必须采取措施保护专利技术。
